ding one-dimensional eigenspace has to\nconsist of the constant functions and to be a subset of the domain of\ndefinition of a certain fractional power of $B$. We are able to show general\nexistence, uniqueness, and regularity results for both these cases, as well as\nfor both the viscous and the nonviscous system.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2018 16:09:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Oct 2018 15:59:48 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 21 Oct 2018 13:20:22 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Fri, 2 Aug 2019 07:27:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-08-05"}
