)\nfluctuations. Our paper presents a new mechanism for generating coherent\nphonons from long-range interactions (coherent long-range interaction induced\nphonons) that does not require the existence of multiple bands to act as\nintermediary states for quasiparticles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Apr 2018 17:59:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 28 Jun 2019 20:09:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-03"}
